Ask HN: Which US bank for multi-currency accounts?
text:
Hi HN,

Just wanted to ask some feedback from you since we are an (ex)-SVB customer who used their multi-currency accounts.

Which bank do you use for multi-currency accounts? What are the fees and fx-rates typically?

We are looking for an option but it seems many of the major banks do not offer currency accounts that are registered in the US.

How to Pass Salesforce OmniStudio-Developer Certification Exam?
text:
Passing the Salesforce OmniStudio-Developer certification exam requires thorough preparation and knowledge of the exam topics. Here are some steps that can help you prepare for and pass the exam:

1: Understand the Exam Objectives: The first step to passing the Salesforce OmniStudio-Developer certification exam is to understand the exam objectives. This will help you to know what you need to study and how to prepare for the exam. 2: Review Exam Study Materials: Salesforce provides official study materials that can help you prepare for the exam. These materials include online training, study guides, and practice exams.

Show HN: AI Chat Bestie – Enhanced UI for ChatGPT API
text:
Been working on this since last week and glad to share it here and now!

There's already been a few other takes on this idea, but I figured none would fit me as well as if I had just built it myself.

All messages are sent and stored locally in the browser for privacy and speed. Accounts are optional and upgrading is a one-time deal.

Any questions, comments, feedback, please, I'd like to hear it all!
